In the future, if you get into a similar situation, consider asking someone higher level for an assist - granted, many of 'em will be busy, some (sigh) may even be rude, but there are sufficient nice people around who are willing to give a new person a hand.<br>
<br>
If you're anything like me, you probably would rather not bother them.  Trust me on this one though - these days, a truly new person in EQ is like a breath of fresh air.<br>
