<br>
Get used to the fact the dieing in EQ has a very harsh penalty.  Basically, you want to adventure and have fun etc while dieing VERY little now that you are past lvl 10.  Be cautious...you can scout most areas while invis or with the SUPER usefull spell eye of zomm, conning mobs as you look around, to see if you will get killed by going there.<br>
<br>
I hope that you are getting in groups some by now.  If not, you should be.  You NEED to learn what you can/should do in groups. It's more important than what you can do solo, in the long run.  It's much better to learn how to be a good group mage at lvl 12 than lvl 40 or 55....<br>
<br>
